{"tid":2438540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人記得蘋果日報漫畫《打妖王》","createTime":"2021-03-08T14:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T15:10:28.000Z","uid":273248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45532d2aaeca05826ccc0509485145d4016281cd","tid":2438540,"uid":273248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:37:52.000Z","msg":"淨係search到呢條link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fmyeah.com/%E6%89%93%E5%A6%96%E7%8E%8B-304.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmyeah.com%2F%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A6%2596%25E7%258E%258B-304.html&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=d33e1f71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fmyeah.com/%E6%89%93%E5%A6%96%E7%8E%8B-304.html</a><br />\n<br />\n妖魔隨流星襲香港，吳空誓做打妖王。<br />\n打妖王是漫畫，亦是一款線上遊戲，為配合漫畫推出，新城電台與蘋果日報漫畫組聯合推出該漫畫之廣播劇，此原聲專輯是非賣品，隨漫畫及蘋果日報免費派發。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4bgiWtE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4bgiWtE.jpg&h=69c2fe39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da2539384818e4f153dd545aeb1dfb8a0f09b389","tid":2438540,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:40:14.000Z","msg":"有啲印象<br />\n<br />\n不過冇睇過"},{"pid":"7d3650e2c0fb44d2bf1c8a43f6d00ebc6b6b2536","tid":2438540,"uid":273248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da2539384818e4f153dd545aeb1dfb8a0f09b389","tid":2438540,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:40:14.000Z","msg":"有啲印象<br />\n<br />\n不過冇睇過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"果陣仲有送一副立體眼鏡睇有少少立體"},{"pid":"ff964b1cd54b27a15be68cbeb25653253bdbf500","tid":2438540,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:46:16.000Z","msg":"記得，仲日日追，阿公仲特登去拎咗隻謝霆鋒、吳嘉莉唱嘅主題曲CD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後嚟打豬八戒變咗單行本定乜就冇再睇"},{"pid":"ae529a122e7ea5124a93ec56dd23b96b3127a31d","tid":2438540,"uid":273248,"like":0,"dislike":0